{"tid":462852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【星島日報】：周永康在獄中研讀佛學的跟隨釋迦牟尼，改名【釋永康】。","createTime":"2017-11-09T02:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T03:34:02.000Z","uid":5812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f423f04784fb9f2fef618bd1b0e2e699cbcb9a22","tid":462852,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/09/105218_22c8cd65f39366e66d394abd04c5b9d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2F105218_22c8cd65f39366e66d394abd04c5b9d5.jpg&h=bde6a665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周永康透露自己較入獄前瘦了3至4公斤，相信原因是在獄中吃營養餐，食物較清淡。被問到潛修佛學的周永康是否已改名「釋永康」，他澄清自己確有學佛，但未有改姓，「我都係跟阿爸姓」，不知道相關報道來源。他又補充可能是黃之鋒、羅冠聰等人在Facebook上的開玩笑言論。"},{"pid":"e7446e6bf7c8c488f6f94ba3d5949ecc848afa82","tid":462852,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"法號係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdf3c382fd1356ed9afacb763ffa09eeb3025a3","tid":462852,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法號係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n永康"},{"pid":"5d338aa09b889e4044140f4e7acf43bbe1aab8ab","tid":462852,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e0d3cabbad8fea86784feff5391ec1c49da452f","tid":462852,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"永康大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}